title: Parental support linked to how well millennials transition to college life

title_detail.value: Parental support linked to how well millennials transition to college life

summary: Researchers show that how well parents or guardians support millennials' psychological needs prior to their transition to college is an important predictor of their psychological well-being as they adapt to college life.
